actions-list.actionItem: Pursuant to the order of Thursday, January 22, 2026,  the      Journal of the proceedings of the Senate was deemed approved to date.
Pursuant to the order of Thursday, January 22, 2026,      the morning hour being deemed expired, and the times for the recognition      of the two leaders being reserved.
The following transactions of morning business occurred on today      .
By unanimous consent, on the request of Ms. Collins, at          3:15 p.m., the Senate adjourned, under its order of today, until          3 p.m. tomorrow.
